freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Late Wednesday night and Thursday, chest pains when breathing, esp when exhaling. A temperature of 99.9 and was feeling very weak. I was very pale. the cardiologist did an ekg and a scan. The BP dropped to 102/32. Friday I felt a bit better. Now fine
